      "parameters" : {
         "def" : [ {
            "localId" : "216",
            "locator" : "40:1-40:54",
            "name" : "ContextPrescriptions",
            "accessLevel" : "Public",
            "annotation" : [ {
               "type" : "Annotation",
               "s" : {
                  "r" : "216",
                  "s" : [ {
                     "value" : [ "/*\n**\n**  Recommendation #6\n**    When opioids are needed for acute pain, clinicians should prescribe no greater quantity than \n**    needed for the expected duration of pain severe enough to require opioids \n**    (recommendation category: A; evidence type: 4).\n**\n**  When\n**    Provider is prescribing an opioid analgesic with ambulatory misuse potential in the outpatient setting\n**    Prescription is for treating acute pain.\n**    CDC 2022 guideline general inclusion criteria met for this patient:\n**      Patient is 18 or over\n**      Patient does not have evidence of sickle cell disease\n**      Patient does not have findings indicating limited life expectancy\n**      Patient does not have orders for therapies indicating end of life care\n**      Patient is not undergoing active cancer treatment:\n**        Patient has had at least 2 office visits within the past 12 months with an oncology specialist present, or\n**        Patient has had at least 2 office visits within the past 12 months with a CDC malignant cancer condition diagnosis\n**      Patient does not have conditions likely terminal for opioid prescribing present\n**    Prescription is for more than 7 days\n**  Then\n**    When Treating Acute Pain, Prescribe No Greater Quantity Than Needed:\n**      Document - Will adjust opioid order\n**      Snooze - Benefits of opioid therapy duration outweigh risks, snooze 3 months\n**      Snooze - N/A see comment, snooze 3 months\n**\n*/\n\n// META: Plan Definition: http://fhir.org/guides/cdc/opioid-cds-r4/PlanDefinition/opioid-cds-06\n\n","parameter ","ContextPrescriptions"," " ]
                  }, {
                     "r" : "217",
                     "s" : [ {
                        "value" : [ "List<" ]
                     }, {
                        "r" : "218",
                        "s" : [ {
                           "value" : [ "MedicationRequest" ]
                        } ]
                     }, {
                        "value" : [ ">" ]
                     } ]
                  } ]
               }
            } ],
            "parameterTypeSpecifier" : {
               "localId" : "217",
               "locator" : "40:32-40:54",
